  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For your consideration - a precision game on rails that brings arcade action into the modern era. Mix <strong>bullet hell</strong>, <strong>dodge 'em up</strong>, and <strong>slippery physics</strong>, and you get a brand new challenge that is as simple as it is difficult. Easy to learn - hold the button to go forward, let go to drift backward - and tough as nails to complete. Face a relentless barrage of endless combinations of attacks, every level being like sneaking through a machine <strong>designed to grind you into a pulp</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869020/extras/2762c12ab462d0e696a95d2fb5f101aa.poster.avif?t=1768601237\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869020/extras/2762c12ab462d0e696a95d2fb5f101aa.webm?t=1768601237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869020/extras/2762c12ab462d0e696a95d2fb5f101aa.mp4?t=1768601237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now there's an even better Cakefoot, featuring 30+ achievements, new visuals, expanded soundtrack, and detailed stats. Zig and zag your way through four chapters of <strong>non-stop action</strong>, <strong>lightning</strong> <strong>quick respawn</strong>, and <strong>compelling level design</strong> that keeps you insisting on just one last try! And don't forget arcade mode - get as far as you can before time expires, and submit your name to the scoreboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869020/extras/8ec4dce9ac2f90cdf8a25e8c2cc35611.poster.avif?t=1768601237\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869020/extras/8ec4dce9ac2f90cdf8a25e8c2cc35611.webm?t=1768601237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869020/extras/8ec4dce9ac2f90cdf8a25e8c2cc35611.mp4?t=1768601237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CAKE is just the beginning -- beat the game and collect all the coins to unlock BEEF CAKE, BUFFALO BEEF CAKE, and even visual effects, MIRROR and WARPED. Cakefoot is the perfect companion to <strong>relentless gaming</strong>! Sally forth today 🐴</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869020/extras/169a49d17a91850c17928fe5fc03d192.poster.avif?t=1768601237\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869020/extras/169a49d17a91850c17928fe5fc03d192.webm?t=1768601237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869020/extras/169a49d17a91850c17928fe5fc03d192.mp4?t=1768601237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Cakefoot Features</u></strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 22-level Quest Mode </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Arcade mode </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >30+ achievements and detailed stats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Modular enemy types that combine into endless patterns </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto-save</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Unlock new difficulties, character skin, and visual effects by collecting challenge coins </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Runs on Windows, Mac, Linux at 60 FPS in any resolution </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Supports mouse, keyboard, and gamepad </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Can run fullscreen, and can be displayed on any monitor in a multi-monitor setup </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dynamically resize the window to any dimension </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Simple JSON syntax for creating and sharing new levels and reskins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Modifiable source code</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869020/extras/1500a990b036de6507b7f3cdc4b0c487.apng?t=1768601237\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869020/extras/1500a990b036de6507b7f3cdc4b0c487.poster.avif?t=1768601237\" class=\"bb_img\" width=20 height=20 /></picture></span> ✨</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For your consideration - a precision game on rails that brings arcade action into the modern era. Mix <strong>bullet hell</strong>, <strong>dodge 'em up</strong>, and <strong>slippery physics</strong>, and you get a brand new challenge that is as simple as it is difficult. Easy to learn - hold the button to go forward, let go to drift backward - and tough as nails to complete. Face a relentless barrage of endless combinations of attacks, every level being like sneaking through a machine <strong>designed to grind you into a pulp</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869020/extras/2762c12ab462d0e696a95d2fb5f101aa.poster.avif?t=1768601237\" width=720 height=404 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869020/extras/2762c12ab462d0e696a95d2fb5f101aa.webm?t=1768601237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869020/extras/2762c12ab462d0e696a95d2fb5f101aa.mp4?t=1768601237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now there's an even better Cakefoot, featuring 30+ achievements, new visuals, expanded soundtrack, and detailed stats. Zig and zag your way through four chapters of <strong>non-stop action</strong>, <strong>lightning</strong> <strong>quick respawn</strong>, and <strong>compelling level design</strong> that keeps you insisting on just one last try! And don't forget arcade mode - get as far as you can before time expires, and submit your name to the scoreboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869020/extra