uns on Windows, Mac, Linux at 60 FPS in any resolution </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Supports mouse, keyboard, and gamepad </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Can run fullscreen, and can be displayed on any monitor in a multi-monitor setup </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Dynamically resize the window to any dimension </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Simple JSON syntax for creating and sharing new levels and reskins</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Modifiable source code</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869020/extras/1500a990b036de6507b7f3cdc4b0c487.apng?t=1768601237\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2869020/extras/1500a990b036de6507b7f3cdc4b0c487.poster.avif?t=1768601237\" class=\"bb_img\" width=20 height=20 /></picture></span> ✨</p>",
